            <title>[GROOVY-2801] Override toString in coerced Map fails for interfaces but is ok for concrete classes</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-2801</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;See &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.nabble.com/can%27t-override-toString-in-coerced-Map...-some-of-the-time-td16990877.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://www.nabble.com/can%27t-override-toString-in-coerced-Map...-some-of-the-time-td16990877.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
